snippet.textDisplay:
My friend breezed through Sekiro and didn't understand why everyone was calling it a hard game. It turns out she had accidentally started overdosing on her lithium medication (as caffeine can make it linger in your body for longer than normal without you realizing it), and one of the side effects of overdosing on lithium is increased reaction speeds.

Don't try this as a pro-strat for Sekiro by the way, she was like a hair away from fucking up her kidneys and needing to go in for dialysis.
